description: You Sly Dog is a locally owned food truck that brings the Tucson community a new twist to some of your favorite hotdog originals. Their menu features their signature take on dogs, sausages, and brats, including The Baloney Tony, made with a premium all beef hot dog surrounded by tasty fried beef bologna placed in a super soft Mexican roll and topped with all your favorite sandwich fixings and a super secret dressing.
name: You Sly Dog
